  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Enerdusk\"</strong> is a roguelike deck-building game where you create strategies centered around units while utilizing cards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards empower your units, and in turn, the enhanced units strengthen your deck and tip the battle in your favor. Activate unit skills with the effects of cards and items to turn the tide of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you can recruit various companions (units), and the player can form a team of up to four units to take into battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each companion is powered by cards and uses unique skills. Find victory through clever combinations of cards and units.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even during battles, you can add new cards to your deck by using cards from your backpack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some unit skills allow you to remove unnecessary cards, enabling quick deck adjustments mid-combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play higher-quality hands and unleash powerful skills against your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies use always-visible enemy cards to deal damage to your units. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since enemy cards are constantly revealed, it’s up to you to decide whether to attack, defend, or strengthen your deck. Your choices and decisions will determine the flow of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras_big/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through events, companions can acquire and equip various items. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the optimal combinations between your units and your deck to build the ultimate party!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Enerdusk\"</strong> is a roguelike deck-building game where you create strategies centered around units while utilizing cards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cards empower your units, and in turn, the enhanced units strengthen your deck and tip the battle in your favor. Activate unit skills with the effects of cards and items to turn the tide of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you can recruit various companions (units), and the player can form a team of up to four units to take into battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each companion is powered by cards and uses unique skills. Find victory through clever combinations of cards and units.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even during battles, you can add new cards to your deck by using cards from your backpack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some unit skills allow you to remove unnecessary cards, enabling quick deck adjustments mid-combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play higher-quality hands and unleash powerful skills against your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies use always-visible enemy cards to deal damage to your units. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since enemy cards are constantly revealed, it’s up to you to decide whether to attack, defend, or strengthen your deck. Your choices and decisions will determine the flow of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras_big/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through events, companions can acquire and equip various items. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the optimal combinations between your units and your deck to build the ultimate party!</p>",
